#

Mushroom Swiss Burger

30 min
$12.5
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-Free OptionHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

BeefComfort FoodQuick Meal

Description

Juicy beef burger topped with sautéed mushrooms and melted Swiss cheese, served on a toasted bun.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 pound
  • burger buns: 4
  • swiss cheese slices: 4
  • fresh mushrooms, sliced: 8 ounces
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
